<?php ?><h1><?php echo $this->Title;?></h1><p>You have successfully launched the first very simple example. Cheers!</p><p><b>MvcCore</b> framework version: <code><b>&quot;<?php echo $this->Version;?>&quot;</b></code></p><p>
